				<p class="text-gray-400 font-bold text-[17px]">Founded in 2011, Loopstudios has been producing world-cass <br> virtual reality projects for some of the best companies around the <br> globe. Our award-winning creations have transformed <br> businesses through digital experiences that bind to their brand.</p>				
			</div>
		</div>
